Query.CellId.name: cell_id
Query.CellId.description: E-UTRAN Cell Identity as a bit string (size (28)), as defined in ETSI TS 136 413

Query.ErabGbrDl.name: erab_gbr_dl
Query.ErabGbrDl.description: Guaranteed downlink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in ETSI TS 123 401

Query.ErabGbrUl.name: erab_gbr_ul
Query.ErabGbrUl.description: Guaranteed uplink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in ETSI TS 123 401

Query.Qci.description: QoS Class Identifier as defined in ETSI TS 123 401

Query.TempUeId.name: temp_ue_id
Query.TempUeId.description: The temporary identifier allocated for the specific UE as defined in ETSI TS 136 413

Problem.type.description: A URI reference according to IETF RFC 3986 that identifies the problem type

Problem.title.description: A short, human-readable summary of the problem type

Problem.status.description: The HTTP status code for this occurrence of the problem

Problem.detail.description: A human-readable explanation specific to this occurrence of the problem

Problem.instance.description: A URI reference that identifies the specific occurrence of the problem

S1UeInfo.description: The information on users per cell.

S1BearerInfoDetailed.description: Information on UEs in the specific cell.

ErabId.description: The element that uniquely identifies a S1 bearer for a specific UE, as defined in ETSI TS 136 413

Mmec.description: MMEC as defined in ETSI TS 136 413

Mtmsi.description: M-TMSI as defined in ETSI TS 136 413

ipAddress.description: eNB transport layer address of this S1 bearer.

tunnelId.description: eNB GTP-U TEID of this S1 bearer.

ipAddress.description: SGW transport layer address of this S1 bearer.

tunnelId.description: SGW GTP-U TEID of this S1 bearer.

seconds.description: The seconds part of the time. Time is defined as Unix-time since January 1, 1970, 00:00:00 UTC

nanoSeconds.description: The nanoseconds part of the time. Time is defined as Unix-time since January 1, 1970, 00:00:00 UTC

AppInsId.description: Unique identifier for the mobile edge application instance

RequestId.description: Unique identifier allocated by the Mobile Edge application for the  Information request.

CellUserInfo.description: The information on users per cell.

Ecgi.description: E-UTRAN CelI Global Identifier as defined in 3GPP TS 36.413

mcc.description: The Mobile Country Code part of PLMN Identity as defined in 3GPP TS 36.413

mnc.description: The Mobile Network Code part of PLMN Identity as defined in 3GPP TS 36.413

CellId.description: The E-UTRAN Cell Identity as a bit string (size (28)), as defined in 3GPP TS 36.413

UeInfo.description: Information on UEs in the specific cell.

type.description: Numeric value (0-255) corresponding to specified type of identifier

Qci.description: QoS Class Identifier as defined in TS 23.401

erabMbrDl.description: This IE indicates the maximum downlink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in TS 23.401 for this bearer.

erabMbrUl.description: This IE indicates the maximum uplink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in TS 23.401 for this bearer.

erabGbrDl.description: This IE indicates the guaranteed  downlink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in TS 23.401 for this bearer.

erabGbrUl.description: This IE indicates the guaranteed  uplink E-RAB Bit Rate as defined in TS 23.401 for this bearer.

CallbackReference.description: URL selected by the Mobile Edge application to receive notifications on the subscribed RNIS information.

Link.description: List of hyperlinks related to the resource

LinkList.description: List of hyperlinks related to the resource

SubscriptionType.description: Numeric value corresponding to specified type of subscription.

FilterCriteriaAssoc.description: List of filtering criteria for the subscription.

FilterCriteriaAssocQci.description: List of filtering criteria for the subscription.

FilterCriteriaAssocHo.description: List of filtering criteria for the subscription.

FilterCriteriaAssocTri.description: List of filtering criteria for the subscription.

S1BearerSubscriptionCriteria.description: List of filtering criteria for the subscription.

HoStatus.description: Description of the subscribed to event

Trigger.description: Unique identifier for the mobile edge application instance

ErabQosParameters_qci.description: QoS Class Identifier as defined in TS 23.401
